<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="18Apr1930"><font color="red">18 April 1930</font> <i>BLHW</i> (to Harriet Weaver from Lucia Joyce): He finished his visits to Dr Pagenstecher to-day who confirms in every point the opinion of Dr Vogt of Zurich &hellip; He has arranged an appointment with Dr [?] Personne(?) the most famous eye doctor in Paris for Wednesday and unless his opinion is in reasonable contradiction he is inclined to return to Zurich as soon as possible for the 1st operation for which it seems special instruments have to be made. We expect to reach Paris on monday night </div>
